tool_description: All data from Turkish Super League 2020-21 season
name: Turkish Super League 2020-21

api_list.name: Goals of season
api_list.description: You can get all goal data of the current season.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://turkish-super-league-2020-21.p.rapidapi.com/api/Goal"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "turkish-super-league-2020-21.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
